   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Crecemos</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Born in 1993, CRECEMOS translated as &quot;Growing Together&quot;, is a community based organization that has served the academic, nutritional and social needs of the community in the semi-urban and &#x200B;rural areas near the city of Oaxaca, Mexico with dedication, intelligence and hope.

Today, Crecemos serves roughly 500 children and their families every year with a wide range of programs and services. We, at AVSI-USA, are very committed to a long-term partnership with Crecemos&apos; mission by supporting their capacity building efforts along the path toward greater financial sustainability and broadening &#x200B;the impact of their work via a donor network called OPPORTUNITY.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The program areas include:
- Supporting the school
- Nutrition Education
- Athletics and Personal Development
- Educational Centers</narrative>
  </description>
